### Email Tracking
@baseUrl = https://api.costkatana.com/api
@apiKey = your_api_key

### Send Report Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/email/report
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"recipient": "user@example.com", "reportType": "weekly"}

### Get Email History
GET {{baseUrl}}/email/history
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
